			num6 = 1.0 + num;

			num6 = 1.0 + num;
			num7 = -2.0 * Math.Cos(d);
			num8 = 1.0 - num;

		case 2:
			num3 = (1.0 - Math.Cos(d)) / 2.0;
			num4 = 1.0 - Math.Cos(d);
			num5 = (1.0 - Math.Cos(d)) / 2.0;
			num6 = 1.0 + num;
			num7 = -2.0 * Math.Cos(d);

			num4 = -2.0 * Math.Cos(d);

	public void UART_RxCmdProcessor(byte rx)
	{
		SetTextCallback setTextCallback = setText;

		{
			switch (rxstate)
			{
			case 0:
				if (rx == byte.MaxValue)
				{
					rxstate = 1;
				}
				break;
			case 1:
				if (rx == 85)
				{
					rxstate = 2;
				}
				break;
			case 2:
				msglen = rx;
				TuningCmdBuffer[0] = rx;
				rxstate = 3;
				TuningCmdCnt = 1;
				break;
			case 3:
				TuningCmdBuffer[TuningCmdCnt] = rx;
				TuningCmdCnt++;
				if (TuningCmdCnt >= msglen + 1)
				{
					UCTRL_CmdProcessor();
					rxstate = 0;
				}
				break;
			}
		}
	}

	public void UartHeartBeatTimerFun(string TEXT)
	{
		if (connectAgain)
		{
			MyProject.Forms.SystemForm.RecallModeFlag = true;
			connectAgain = false;
			Connect_Click();
		}
		if (EQChanged)
		{
			SaveControlPara();
			EQChanged = false;
		}
		checked
		{
			UartHeartBeatTimer_Cnt++;
			if (UartHeartBeatTimer_Cnt >= 200)
			{
				UartHeartBeatTimer_Cnt = 200;
			}
			if (RxFinish)
			{
				RxFinish_Cnt++;
				if (RxFinish_Cnt >= 200)
				{
					RxFinish_Cnt = 200;
				}
			}
			if (DelayReceive)
			{
				DelayReceiveCnt++;
				if (DelayReceiveCnt > 21)
				{
					DelayReceiveCnt = 0;
					HeartBeatDisCnt = 2;
					DelayReceive = false;
				}
			}
			if (!((RxFinish_Cnt > 3) & (UartHeartBeatTimer_Cnt >= 1)))
			{
				return;
			}
			byte[] buf = new byte[4] { 3, 48, 0, 33 };
			UartHeartBeatTimer_Cnt = 0;
			SendEnable = true;
			RxCnt = 0;
			UartRxState = byte.MaxValue;
			TmpBuf[0] = 0;
			ControlInited = false;
			UartHeartTest = true;
			CommandSend(buf);
			ControlInited = true;
			Thread.Sleep(100);
			UartHeartTest = false;
			if ((TmpBuf[0] == byte.MaxValue) & (TmpBuf[1] == 85) & (TmpBuf[2] == 3) & (TmpBuf[3] == 48))
			{
				DisCnt = 0;
			}
			else
			{
				DisCnt++;
			}
			if (DisCnt >= HeartBeatDisCnt)
			{
				Uart_OK = false;
				if (SerialPort1.IsOpen)
				{
					SerialPort1.Close();
				}
				RxFinish = false;
				RxFinish_Cnt = 0;
				DisCnt = 0;
			}
			else
			{
				Uart_OK = true;
			}
			((Form)MyProject.Forms.MainForm).Text = SysName + "" + (Uart_OK ? "" : "");
		}
	}
